title: december 4: i’m just a dinosaur (egg)
description:
Today on the pod, Maia delves into a tale of 22 dinosaur eggs found in China and their fraudulent auction in Los Angeles. Then Maia chats about a silly moment of a US president trying to get down with youth culture.
